<div class="com-share" data-id="13724" data-title="《拍电影造乐园要花不少钱，于是华谊找来了平安银行这个金主》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13724/medium/13724.jpg?1439954181" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13724.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
